snippet.title: Drawception #1 - Drawing The Joker in 10 Minutes!
snippet.description:
A little trial run of recording some Drawception game-play!
Special thanks to Carlos for helping me set this up:  https://pastebin.com/1qH2np94

Please consider watching in HD!

Using ANBT Drawception Script: https://drawception.com/forums/general/11830/anbt-enhancement-script-for-drawception/ 
Finished game: https://drawception.com/game/b856Q69KzM/joker-with-cheshire-cat-picture/
Music: https://audionautix.com/

I hope you enjoyed!
